---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Highlight from "../components/highlight.jsx";
---

<Layout title="Devops Engineer & CS Enthusiast">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 min-h-[80vh]">
    <header class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Hi, I'm toto</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Devops Engineer & CS Enthusiast</p>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">About Me</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
          I'm passionate about creating beautiful and functional <Highlight color="blue">websites</Highlight> or <Highlight color="purple">Mobile App</Highlight>. 
          With a keen eye for design and a love for clean code, I bring ideas to life in the digital realm.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">What I'm Learning</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
          I believe in continuous learning and expanding my skillset. Currently, I'm:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Working as a  <Highlight color="green">Devops</Highlight></li>
          <li>Developing <Highlight color="purple">mobile applications</Highlight> (sometimes)</li>
          <li>Exploring the fascinating world of <Highlight color="red">machine learning</Highlight></li>
          <li>Staying updated with the latest web technologies (mostly)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          My curiosity drives me to constantly learn and grow in this ever-evolving field of technology.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/togido.xyz" target="_blank" class="inline-block bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-600 dark:hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded transition duration-300">
        Get in Touch (<s>on twitter</s> Bluesky )
      </a>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>

